      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in fair condition, and we want to give you a complete and transparent picture before you consider purchasing. The exterior shows visible wear \u2014 expect fading paint, some scratches, and minor dents that are noticeable upon close inspection. The interior has seen regular use, with worn upholstery, some scuffs on the dashboard, and general signs of age. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but you should anticipate that some components are showing their age and may require attention in the near future \u2014 we recommend a pre-purchase inspection so you know exactly what you're getting into. This is a solid option for a buyer looking for a functional, everyday vehicle at a reasonable price, with the understanding that it is not without its flaws.",
