    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in true mint condition \u2014 a designation we apply only when a car genuinely earns it, and this one does so without question. The exterior is essentially flawless: the paint retains a deep, vibrant luster with no fading, scratches, chips, or blemishes of any kind. Panel gaps are tight and uniform, and all trim pieces, moldings, and chrome accents are pristine. The interior is equally impressive \u2014 the upholstery shows no wear, cracking, or staining, the carpets are clean, and every surface looks as though it just left the showroom floor. All electronics, controls, and features function perfectly, from the infotainment system to the climate controls. Under the hood, the engine is clean and well-maintained, running smoothly with no leaks, unusual noises, or warning lights. Service history is up to date, and the car has been carefully kept throughout its life. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that truly lives up to the 'mint' label \u2014 ideal for a buyer who wants the best without compromise.",
      "price": 45000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
