      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in mint condition \u2014 an exceptionally well-preserved example that stands out even among carefully maintained used cars. The exterior is virtually flawless, with paint that retains a deep, glossy finish free of scratches, chips, or swirl marks. Body panels are straight and true, with no signs of prior collision repair or rust. The interior is equally impressive, presenting like new with no wear on the seats, carpets, or trim surfaces \u2014 everything looks and feels as though it just left the showroom floor. Mechanically, this car is in top-notch shape: all systems function perfectly, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, and there are no warning lights, leaks, or unusual noises. Service records are up to date, and the vehicle has been meticulously cared for throughout its life. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a used vehicle that truly requires nothing \u2014 you can drive it home with complete confidence and zero reservations.",
